"What is the unit of momentum?","kg m/s.","Forces"
"What is the conservation of momentum?","Total momentum before = total momentum after, in a closed system.","Forces"
"What is an elastic collision?","Total kinetic energy is conserved.","Forces"
"What is an inelastic collision?","Kinetic energy is not conserved (some becomes heat/sound).","Forces"
"What is stopping distance?","Thinking distance + braking distance.","Forces"
"What factors increase thinking distance?","Tiredness, alcohol/drugs, distractions, higher speed.","Forces"
"What factors increase braking distance?","Higher speed, wet/icy roads, worn brakes/tyres, greater mass.","Forces"
